<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your Services Are Under Review</title>

    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap");

      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin: auto;
      }

      h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #333;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      ul {
        text-align: left;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }

      li {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .footer {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <h2>🔍 Your Services Are Under Review</h2>
      <p>Dear <strong><%= vendorName %></strong>,</p>
      <p>
        Thank you for listing your services on Evaga Entertainment! 🎉 Our team
        is currently reviewing your profile to ensure quality standards.
      </p>
      <p><strong>📌 Audit Process:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>✅ Reviewing your service details</li>
        <li>✅ Checking compliance with marketplace guidelines</li>
        <li>✅ Approving your profile within 24 hours</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We will notify you once your services are live on the platform!</p>
      <p class="footer">
        Best Regards,<br />
        Evaga Vendor Support<br />
        📞 +91 8296157611 | 📧
        <a href="mailto:info@evagaentertainment.com"
          >info@evagaentertainment.com</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
